*
*TEST.CMD
*
STORE 'C:TESTFILE' TO USEFILE
SET TALK OFF
* TURN ON FILE LOCKING
POKE 8,1
* CREATE AN INFINITE LOOP
STORE -1 TO ALL
DO WHILE ALL <> 0
  STORE -1 TO LOCK  DO WHILE LOCK <> 0
    * BE SURE TESTFILE.CMD IS ON DRIVE C:
